The paper discusses communication and networking in the terahertz frequency band, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), electromagnetic theory (cs.EM), multimedia (cs.MM), and network architecture and analysis (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
